description:
Estimated gasoline sales data is derived from New York State
Department of Taxation and Finance data on gasoline sales and
gasoline sales tax collections. Gasoline sales data is estimated for each
county with the exception that individual county data for New York
City is not available. Data is weighted for regional price differences
and differing county tax rates.
